      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a good starting point, but it's a bit generic. To really tailor the marketing campaign, I need more specifics on the actual demographics. Can you get more granular? I'm thinking about things like age, nationality, ethnicity, and even where they typically spend their time or what their social circles look like. What kind of specific profile are we looking at for this level of luxury?",
