      "content": "Interesting. So you're saying the core market is basically just Western/European? That feels a bit narrow for a global luxury brand. What about the massive influx of wealth coming from emerging markets in Asia, the Middle East, or other regions? Don't those groups represent a huge part of the high-end watch market now, or do they not fit the \"ideal\" profile you're describing?",
